<div class="container marketing">

    <!-- Three columns of text below the carousel -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-4">
            <img class="img-circle" src="~/FinalWebPhotos/Projects.jpg" alt="Generic placeholder image" width="260" height="140">
            <div>
                <h2>My Projects</h2>
            </div>
            <p>I'm not quite sure if I added enough links to my projects</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="/Projects" role="button">My Projects &raquo;</a></p>
        </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
        <div class="col-lg-4">
            <img class="img-circle" src="~/FinalWebPhotos/AboutMe.jpg" alt="Generic placeholder image" width="260" height="140">
            <h2>About</h2>
            <p>So maybe I'll just add another link to my about page</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="/Home/About" role="button">About Me &raquo;</a></p>
        </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
        <div class="col-lg-4">
            <img class="img-circle" src="~/Content/BlurredSelfie.jpg" alt="Generic placeholder image" width="260" height="140">
            <h2>Contact</h2>
            <p>I guess it wouldn't hurt to add one more link to my contact page</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="/Home/Contact" role="button">Contact Me &raquo;</a></p>
        </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
    </div><!-- /.row -->
    